long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Helping you gather data for your Youtube channel to accelerate your growth.

Features:

Copy channel video performance from Social Blade.

Navigate to a channel page in Social Blade and click on "User Videos" (https://socialblade.com/youtube/c/businessfilmboothonline/videos)
Open the plugin and then click "Scrape Results"
Copy these into a spreadsheet to compare the performance of different channels.
